Package: crosstabr
Type: Package
Title: Cross tabulation for HTML and Markdown
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-11-13
Authors@R: person("Thomas", "Klebel", email = "t.klebel@icloud.com",
          role = c("cre", "aut"))
Description: Cross tabulation for HTML and Markdown. This packages offers
    cross tabulation in a new way: You can use layers to customize the output.
    The resulting table is rendered as HTML for better display on small screens.
    Methods for using crosstabr together with RMarkdown will be made available.
LazyData: TRUE
Depends: htmltools
Imports: vcd,
    magrittr,
    assertthat,
    xtable,
    stringr,
    purrr,
    dplyr
RoxygenNote: 5.0.0
